---
title: Creamy Tomato Ravioli with Courgette & Balsamic Rocket
description: You will devour this plant-based mushroom ravioli in seconds when you taste it with a creamy tomato sauce with
hidden leek and courgette. A dressed side of rocket salad adds a touch of freshness to the dish.
